                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090517-55-off319 t18090517-55-cd320"></join>, a pair of stays, value 3 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18090517-55-victim556" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Wood
                  <interp inst="t18090517-55-victim556" type="surname" value="Wood"></interp>
